description:
Note: The mumble talk was almost silent so I amplified it in my editing. Enjoy the loud keyboard clicking and other fun background noises! Most of what was said was too silent for me to hear while playing, so that's why I'm oblivious to some of the conversation.

Survival of the fittest is a modded minecraft PvP/PvE experience put together by BdoubleO. The players are tossed into a post apocalyptic world and are left to loot towns, cities, and structures in order to survive.  The winner/winners are the last players standing.
